OL,3,CNottinghamshire burglar jailed after
OL,4,Cvictim spotted him in social media post
OL,6,FA burglar has been jailed after he was
OL,7,Frecognised by his victim from a social
OL,8,Fmedia post.
OL,10,FAlan Brown, 50, was caught on a home
OL,11,Fsecurity camera as he broke into a
OL,12,Fproperty in Three Tunns Road, in
OL,13,FEastwood, in Nottinghamshire on April
OL,14,F14th last year
OL,16,FBrown's victim rushed to the address
OL,17,Fafter receiving an intruder alert to
OL,18,Fhis mobile phone.
