OL,3,CNottinghamshire burglar jailed after
OL,4,Cvictim spotted him in social media post
OL,6,FThe 50-year-old had already fled the
OL,7,Fscene but was later recognised by his
OL,8,Fvictim from a previous post on a local
OL,9,FFacebook group.
OL,11,FWhen he was arrested two days later,
OL,12,Fhe was still wearing the same
OL,13,Ftracksuit jacket he'd had on during
OL,14,Fthe burglary.
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police, Detective
OL,17,FConstable Liam O'Kane said: "Brown is
OL,18,Fa well-known offender with a high
OL,19,Fnumber of previous convictions.
