OL,3,CNottinghamshire burglar jailed after
OL,4,Cvictim spotted him in social media post
OL,6,F"In this case his notoriety came back
OL,7,Fto bite him when his victim
OL,8,Fimmediately recognised who he was.
OL,10,F"Although it is likely we would have
OL,11,Fcaught up with Brown from other
OL,12,Fevidence, the victim's security
OL,13,Fcameras really made the difference in
OL,14,Fthis case and allowed us to quickly
OL,15,Farrest a suspect and secure vital
OL,16,Fevidence against him.
OL,18,F"I am pleased he has now been returned
OL,19,Fto jail where he can no longer pose a
OL,20,Fthreat to local residents."
