OL,3,CNottinghamshire burglar jailed after
OL,4,Cvictim spotted him in social media post
OL,6,FBrown of Eastwood later pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto burglary.
OL,9,FHe also admitted to an additional
OL,10,Fcharge of theft from a motor vehicle
OL,11,Fafter tools were stolen from a van on
OL,12,FApril 15th.
OL,14,FAppearing at Nottingham Crown Court on
OL,15,FMonday, March 31, Brown was jailed for
OL,16,F15 months.
